reviewText:
Sadly this dvd skipped on almost every short film and is missing the bonus disc "power of nightmares".
Definitely won't ever trust this seller again
I bought this item on a whim several years ago at a street fair in Chicago. It's very entertaining, but might be a bit strange for first-time viewers of the series. Highly entertaining!

There are only two good shorts in this thing and the rest really really suck.  I bought this per a reccomendation from a friend who swears by the series.  It was extremely dissapointing and I actually got accused of having "issues" because I accidently called someone on my cell phone while I was watching one of the shorts and the person I called overheard the conversation from the film and thought it was me talking.  Overall a huge waste of time and money.  You can find way better short films on the internet for free.
